1
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:50,860
The lamp oil

2
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:52,830
has been tampered with.

3
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:57,730
Vice Director Shen,

4
00:00:57,730 --> 00:00:59,190
the Director summons you.

5
00:01:00,130 --> 00:01:00,900
Coming.

6
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:21,260
Director.

7
00:01:21,660 --> 00:01:22,789
Vice Director Shen,

8
00:01:22,860 --> 00:01:24,530
did you rest well last night?

9
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:25,800
That oil lamp

10
00:01:26,060 --> 00:01:28,330
was specially prepared for you.

11
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:30,060
It has a calming effect.

12
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:32,500
Thank you for your kindness, Director.

13
00:01:32,729 --> 00:01:34,330
For today's morning lesson,

14
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:37,400
I will explain the affairs within the tower to you.

15
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,160
Yes,

16
00:01:38,330 --> 00:01:39,000
Director.

17
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:41,300
This is the Ziwei Hall,

18
00:01:41,630 --> 00:01:43,600
where heaven and earth reside.

19
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:47,759
This person

20
00:01:48,530 --> 00:01:49,860
is imitating my father.

21
00:01:51,130 --> 00:01:53,130
You are very knowledgeable, Director.

22
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:54,259
I have learned a lot.

23
00:01:54,460 --> 00:01:57,759
This token allows access to the first to third floors of the Black Tower.

24
00:01:57,759 --> 00:01:59,200
Since you are the Vice Director,

25
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:02,430
you should familiarize yourself with the affairs in the tower.

26
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:03,630
Thank you, Director.

27
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:20,300
Is this

28
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,420
the Blood Pool?

29
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:22,000
No.

30
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,460
This is the Dragon Marrow Pool,

31
00:02:23,460 --> 00:02:25,860
brewed with ninety-nine rare medicinal herbs

32
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,630
to nourish the foundation of the dragon vein.

33
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,360
The dragon vein is deep at the bottom of the pool.

34
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:32,020
New medicine needs to be added every seven days.

35
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,130
Everything is for His Majesty

36
00:02:38,130 --> 00:02:39,990
and for the foundation of Tianqi.

37
00:02:43,260 --> 00:02:44,200
It's dangerous near the pool.

38
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,760
Please stop here, Vice Director Shen.

39
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:46,560
It's alright.

40
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:48,300
You are a sensible man, Vice Director Shen.

41
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:49,900
Your father, Shen Qingshan,

42
00:02:50,130 --> 00:02:51,560
also stood here back then

43
00:02:52,530 --> 00:02:54,860
and strongly agreed with this great cause.

44
00:02:54,860 --> 00:02:55,930
Where is my father

45
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,700
now?

46
00:02:58,100 --> 00:02:59,030
He is down there.

47
00:03:00,330 --> 00:03:02,960
The core of the dragon vein needs someone with a pure Yang destiny to guard it.

48
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,620
Your father

49
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:05,430
went down voluntarily.

50
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,960
I'm sorry, My Lord.

51
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,890
I didn't mean to.

52
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,760
Drag him away.

53
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:30,900
The liquid in the Blood Pool contains sedatives.

54
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:32,600
The Taoists are controlled by the drugs.

55
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,660
The old servant stole blood crystal powder to write a warning.

56
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:37,060
This person must be very close to my father.

57
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:46,329
This stone slab is very hard.

58
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:47,460
To be able to leave marks,

59
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:48,700
requires a lot of strength.

60
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:50,329
A servant suddenly fell ill last night.

61
00:03:50,329 --> 00:03:51,829
The Director has ordered someone to bury him.

62
00:03:51,829 --> 00:03:54,290
You don't need to worry, Vice Director Shen.

63
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:01,930
Calming.

64
00:04:02,230 --> 00:04:03,100
Bewitching.

65
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:24,630
Mo'er,

66
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,690
why haven't you come to save me yet?

67
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,430
You are right here in the tower,

68
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:30,690
but you only care about saving yourself.

69
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,530
Illusion.

70
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:41,330
There's indeed something wrong with the lamp oil.

71
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,330
The sweet-scented base

72
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:45,230
has the same origin as the liquid in the Blood Pool.

73
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:46,030
With the addition of Datura flowers,

74
00:04:46,030 --> 00:04:48,000
the extract causes hallucinations.

75
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,030
The purple sparks suggest

76
00:04:49,030 --> 00:04:50,530
that mineral powder was mixed in.

77
00:04:50,530 --> 00:04:51,830
Heat activates the medicinal properties.

78
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:52,830
That oil lamp

79
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,330
was specially prepared for you.

80
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:56,900
It has a calming effect.
